  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients are required to position prior to retinal detachment surgery. We seek to see whether
      there is a correlation between the performed positioning and retinal detachment
      progression/regression in fovea-on retinal detachment patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
